&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Up to $50K Sign-on Bonus + Relocation Assistance Available!!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Heart + Paw is seeking an experienced Partner Veterinarian for our Partner Hospital, South Peak Veterinary Hospital, located in the vibrant city of Saugerties, NY. This unique opportunity is ideal for veterinarians interested in stepping into a Medical Director role with the option to co-own a full-service veterinary hospital. You’ll enjoy the freedom of practice ownership, with wealth-building potential, without the administrative burden. Join a supportive, veterinarian-led community with Heart + Paw, where our team provides operational backing and a collaborative community to empower your success.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none&quot;&gt;This is petcare reimagined®️.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
