&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Veterinary medical degree with a license in good standing with the applicable state board.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 4-5 years of clinical experience and a strong client-focused approach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated leadership experience and an interest in practice ownership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to build and retain a loyal client base through exceptional service.&lt;/li&gt;
