&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pet Stylist (Groomer)&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Traveling Groomer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$1,000 Sign-On Bonus!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a skilled &lt;strong&gt;Pet Stylist&lt;/strong&gt; with a passion for creating exceptional experiences for pets and their families? We are redefining pet care, and we want you to be part of our team. With a beautifully designed workspace, state-of-the-art tools, and a supportive environment, you’ll have the opportunity to focus on what you do best—providing top-notch grooming services while building meaningful relationships with clients. This is a fully traveling position; the Stylist may be asked to cover multiple centers throughout a single week or be stationed at a specific center for a period of time. The majority of Heart + Paw locations with Style services are within a 90-minute drive of the Greater Philadelphia Area. The Stylist may be asked periodically to travel to other locations within our geographic footprint if there is urgent need.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why You’ll Love Working Here:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of a collaborative, pet-focused team that values your input.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy a modern, thoughtfully designed workspace equipped with the latest technology.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Grow in your career with a company committed to low-stress handling and pet wellness.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities Include:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Delivering professional grooming services tailored to each pet’s needs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and maintaining a loyal client base through excellent service and communication.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applying advanced grooming techniques, including contemporary cuts, coloring, and styling.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with veterinary, daycare, and retail teams to enhance the overall pet care experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining a clean, safe workspace and promoting all center services.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience: 2+ years as a professional groomer.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skills: Expertise in modern grooming practices, animal behavior knowledge, and strong interpersonal abilities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion: A love for pets and the art of grooming.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Physical Stamina: Ability to handle pets of all sizes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial Spirit: Eagerness to grow your client base and contribute to the team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Certifications: Fear Free, HABRI, or Low-Stress Handling certification (preferred).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tech-Savvy: Comfortable using technology to enhance the pet parent experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience grooming cats.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuing education or certifications in pet grooming.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Perks of Joining the Team:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive pay and opportunities for advancement.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a state-of-the-art facility designed with pets, their parents, and our team in mind.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
